metadata.name: Gargoyles
metadata.description:
"Gargoyles"  
Cohesive creatures, carriers of magic and protection, possessing amazing strength, beauty and at the same time terrifying. Their spirit is strong, and their body is wonderful and natural. They come to life under the light of the thinnest moon and guiding star, when there is wet asphalt on the street, and water flows down the branches, illuminating everything around with the lightning of life.
